<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="Aink215-kilavi"> iravukkuṟi nayanta talaimakaḷ pakaṟ kuṟikkaṇ vantu nīṅkuntalaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉākat tōḻikkuc colliyatu.   </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> What the heroine, who desired night trysts, told [her] confidante while the hero, who had left after coming for a day tryst, was behind the hedge.   </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink215">
<l>kaṭṭaḷai yaṉṉa maṇiniṟat tumpi</l>
<l>yiṭṭiya kuyiṉṟa tuṟaivayiṟ celīiyar</l>
<l>taṭṭait taṇṇumaip piṉṉa riyavar</l>
<l>tīṅkuḻa lāmpali ṉiṉiya vimirum</l>
<l>putaṉmalar mālaiyum pirivō</l>
<l>rataṉiṉuṅ koṭiya ceykuva raṉṉāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In order to go to the narrowly constructed ghats</l>
<l>[with] sapphire-hued bees resembling touchstones</l>
<l rend="space">he who departs [as soon as it is] evening </l>
<l rend="indent">when the shrubs blossom, </l>
<l rend="indent">[and] when musicians, </l>
<l rend="indent">following the taṭṭai-device and taṇṇumai drums, </l>
<l rend="indent">play pleasing [melodies] like the Āmpal-tune on a sweet flute,</l>
<l rend="space">would commit acts even more cruel than that, mother! </l>


      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
